tic stub adapter and CLI construction hook are present, and the requested tests exist: [src/adapters/stub_backend.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/adapters/stub_backend.rs#L15), [src/cli/run.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/run.rs#L54), [tests/unit/agent_execution_test.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/agent_execution_test.rs#L167), and [tests/unit/stub_backend_test.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/unit/stub_backend_test.rs#L37).\n\n## Notes\nNo concrete spec gaps, regressions, or pattern violations stood out in the reviewed scope. Verification also passed in the repo dev shell with `cargo test` and `cargo clippy --all-targets --all-features -- -D warnings`.\n\n## Commit Message\nadd agent execution facade with stub backend and session/raw-output persistence"}}
